Package: ctsemgui
Type: Package
Title: GUI-Oriented Model Specification Helpers for ctsem
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Charles", "Driver", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "charles.driver2@uzh.ch")
Author: Charles Driver [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Charles Driver <charles.driver2@uzh.ch>
Description: Provides a small GUI-neutral model specification layer for ctsem.
    The first pass supports matrix-based model editing, structured validation,
    conversion to ctsem model objects, reproducible code export, and a minimal
    Shiny interface built on the same functions.
